@node Annotations
@subsection Annotations

Use the @samp{:annotations:} drawer key to attach annotations to a class:

@example
*** ex:Dog
@comma{}:PROPERTIES:
@comma{}:subclass-of: ex:Animal
@comma{}:END:
@comma{}:annotations:
@comma{}- rdfs:label :: "Dog"@@en
@comma{}- skos:definition :: "A domesticated canine."@@en
@comma{}:end:
@end example

