@node A first SPARQL block
@subsection A first SPARQL block

Add this to @samp{pets.org}@comma{} below the class definitions:

@example
#+begin_src sparql :url "pets.omn"
@comma{}select ?s ?o where @{ ?s rdfs:subClassOf ?o @}
#+end_src
@end example

Press @samp{C-c C-c} inside the block.  ELOT shells out to ROBOT and
inserts the result table below the block.  No @samp{PREFIX} boilerplate
needed --- ELOT injects prefixes from your @samp{prefix-table}.

